    public class MCF1RGImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements MCF1RG
    An implementation of the model object 'MCF1RG'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • CF Lid
    • Sectid
    • CF Name
    • CP Name
    • FCS Name
    • Char Rot
